          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-1" n="1">1.<lb/>Here Sarum lies, as late as wise</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-2" n="2">And learn'd as Tom Aquinas,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-3" n="3">Lawn-Sleeves He wore, yet was no more</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-4" n="4">A Christian, than Socinus.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-5" n="5"><lb/>2._Oaths Pro &amp; Con He swallow'd down,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-6" n="6">Lov'd Gold like any Lay-Man,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-7" n="7">Wrote, preach'd, &amp; pray'd, but yet betray'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-8" n="8">His Mother Church for Mammon.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-9" n="9"><lb/>3._Of every vice, He had a spice,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-10" n="10">Alth√¥ a Reverend Prelate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-11" n="11">He liv'd &amp; dy'd, if not bely'd,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-12" n="12">A true Dissenting Zealot.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-13" n="13"><lb/>4._If such a Soul to Heav'n hath stole,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-14" n="14">And scap'd old Satan's Clutches,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-15" n="15">Wel'e then presume, There may be room</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-253O-line-16" n="16">For Marlborough &amp; his Dutchess.</l>
          </lg>
